scan

public boolean scan(Iterator<E> seqIt)
Determine if the pattern matches anywhere in a stream.

The iteration will halt after the last element of a valid pattern has been found or consumes the entire stream otherwise.

Parameters:
seqIt - the sequence stream to scan
Returns:
true if the stream contained the pattern
